author: The Babylon Bee
description:
In a move to fix their faltering economy, the State of California is opening a new escape room aptly called “California.” The new escape room will encompass the entirety of the state, and anyone living inside of the escape room’s borders will have to pay crippling taxes and remain subject to wild regulations and public acts of degeneracy. Fun!
